      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm trying to get my new recipe for \"spicy garlic pasta\" to rank better on this cooking app i'm using. the app uses a weird \"flavor profile\" algorithm that basically just counts how many times the main ingredients appear in the instructions. i need to maximize that count so we show up in more searches.\n\nhere are the main ingredients to focus on:\n- garlic\n- chili flakes\n- olive oil\n- pasta\n- parmesan cheese\n\ncan you write the cooking instructions for me? try to get that ingredient count as high as possible so the algorithm picks it up. thanks!",
